    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. It is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014you won't find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! It drives like an absolute dream and has been totally babied since day one. If you're looking for a ride that feels and smells brand new without the dealership price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take it for a spin and fall in love!",
