    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Honda S2000 (AP2), a masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the high-revving F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC inline-four, delivering a linear power delivery and an 8,200 RPM redline. The longitudinal front-mid engine orientation achieves a perfect 50/50 weight distribution, paired with an exceptionally rigid X-bone frame and a double-wishbone suspension geometry for surgical turn-in precision. Power is managed via a close-ratio 6-speed manual transmission with short-throw engagement, feeding a Torsen limited-slip differential. This collector-quality unit remains in factory-original configuration, retaining all 10 VIN tags, pristine paint clarity, and an immaculate undercarriage free of oxidation or subframe fatigue. An uncompromising, analog driving machine for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
