    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, powered by the S54B32 straight-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive rear subframe reinforcement and documented rod bearing service. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag 420G manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal traction. Suspension kinematics are factory-spec, offering unparalleled lateral grip and damping characteristics. Every mechanical component, from the high-pressure VANOS lines to the cooling system, has been scrutinized for peak performance. A concours-ready example with zero aesthetic or mechanical compromises.",
